  "body": "### Description\n_Type_: Bug\n_Summary_: when custom mailserver is added and deleted, after tapping on + again details of removed mailserver are shown. At attempt to connect to it \"Warning! Connect to `<no value>`?\" is shown, and if you choose \"Confirm\" > empty mailserver is shown in the list.\n\n#### Expected behavior\nno values are are preserved\n\n#### Actual behavior\nCan see all details of deleted mailserver.\nIf click on connect - \"Warning! Connect to <no value>?\" is shown.\nAfter confirm can see empty mailserver in list, and there is no option to delete it.\n![](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/54748546-3f604580-4bd2-11e9-87ea-f1fa06801ae9.png)\n\n### Reproduction\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n\n* Open Status\n* Go to Mailserver settings\n* Add custom mailserver\n* Tap on it\n* Tap on \"Delete\"\n* Tap on + again (to add custom mailserver)\n\n### Additional Information\n\n\n* Status version: 21/03/2019\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\n\n#### Logs\nVideo: https://take.ms/bnGc6",
